{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Shorten the hours in which fireworks can be set off.",
        "additional_details": "There are many people and animals who are affected by the loud noises fireworks make. They can put people's mental health at risk of triggers and could put a bigger strain on our NHS. Why cause trauma to people's lives for 2 months of the year?",
        "background": "We think that fireworks should only be let off between the hours of 1800-2100 to reduce the stress on animals, children and vulnerable adults.",
